{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Now I'm going to give you a story."},{"time":2000,"text":"It's an Indian story about an Indian woman and her journey."},{"time":5000,"text":"Let me begin with my parents."},{"time":8000,"text":"I'm a product of this"},{"time":10000,"text":"visionary mother and father."},{"time":12000,"text":"Many years ago, when I was born in the '50s --"},{"time":15000,"text":"'50s and '60s"},{"time":17000,"text":"didn't belong to girls in India."},{"time":19000,"text":"They belonged to boys."},{"time":21000,"text":"They belonged to boys who would join business"},{"time":23000,"text":"and inherit business from parents,"},{"time":25000,"text":"and girls would be dolled up to get married."},{"time":27000,"text":"My family, in my city,"},{"time":29000,"text":"and almost in the country, was unique."},{"time":32000,"text":"We were four of us, not one,"},{"time":34000,"text":"and fortunately no boys."},{"time":36000,"text":"We were four girls and no boys."},{"time":38000,"text":"And my parents were part"},{"time":40000,"text":"of a landed property family."},{"time":42000,"text":"My father defied his own grandfather,"},{"time":45000,"text":"almost to the point of disinheritance,"},{"time":47000,"text":"because he decided to educate"},{"time":49000,"text":"all four of us."},{"time":51000,"text":"He sent us to one of the best schools in the city"},{"time":53000,"text":"and gave us the best education."},{"time":55000,"text":"As I've said, when we're born, we don't choose our parents,"},{"time":58000,"text":"and when we go to school, we don't choose our school."},{"time":60000,"text":"Children don't choose a school."},{"time":62000,"text":"They just get the school which parents choose for them."},{"time":64000,"text":"So this is the foundation time which I got."},{"time":67000,"text":"I grew up like this, and so did my other three sisters."},{"time":70000,"text":"And my father used to say at that time,"},{"time":72000,"text":"\"I'm going to spread all my four daughters in four corners of the world.\""},{"time":75000,"text":"I don't know if he really meant [that], but it happened."},{"time":78000,"text":"I'm the only one who's left in India."},{"time":80000,"text":"One is a British, another is an American"},{"time":82000,"text":"and the third is a Canadian."},{"time":84000,"text":"So we are four of us in four corners of the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":87000,"text":"And since I said they're my role models,"},{"time":90000,"text":"I followed two things which my father and mother gave me."},{"time":93000,"text":"One, they said, \"Life is on an incline."},{"time":95000,"text":"You either go up,"},{"time":97000,"text":"or you come down.\""},{"time":99000,"text":"And the second thing, which has stayed with me,"},{"time":101000,"text":"which became my philosophy of life,"},{"time":103000,"text":"which made all the difference,"},{"time":105000,"text":"is: 100 things happen in your life, good or bad."},{"time":108000,"text":"Out of 100, 90 are your creation."},{"time":110000,"text":"They're good. They're your creation. Enjoy it."},{"time":113000,"text":"If they're bad, they're your creation. Learn from it."},{"time":116000,"text":"Ten are nature-sent over which you can't do a thing."},{"time":119000,"text":"It's like a death of a relative,"},{"time":121000,"text":"or a cyclone, or a hurricane, or an earthquake."},{"time":124000,"text":"You can't do a thing about it."},{"time":126000,"text":"You've got to just respond to the situation."},{"time":128000,"text":"But that response comes out of those 90 points."},{"time":131000,"text":"Since I'm a product of this philosophy,"},{"time":133000,"text":"of 90/10,"},{"time":135000,"text":"and secondly, \"life on an incline,\""},{"time":137000,"text":"that's the way I grew up"},{"time":139000,"text":"to be valuing what I got."},{"time":142000,"text":"I'm a product of opportunities,"},{"time":144000,"text":"rare opportunities in the '50s and the '60s,"},{"time":146000,"text":"which girls didn't get,"},{"time":148000,"text":"and I was conscious of the fact that what my parents were giving me"},{"time":150000,"text":"was something unique."},{"time":152000,"text":"Because all of my best school friends were getting dolled up"},{"time":154000,"text":"to get married with a lot of dowry,"},{"time":156000,"text":"and here I was with a tennis racket and going to school"},{"time":159000,"text":"and doing all kinds of extracurricular activities."},{"time":161000,"text":"I thought I must tell you this."},{"time":163000,"text":"Why I said this, is the background."}]},{"cues":[{"time":165000,"text":"This is what comes next."},{"time":167000,"text":"I joined the Indian Police Service as a tough woman,"},{"time":170000,"text":"a woman with indefatigable stamina,"},{"time":172000,"text":"because I used to run for my tennis titles, etc."},{"time":175000,"text":"But I joined the Indian Police Service,"},{"time":178000,"text":"and then it was a new pattern of policing."},{"time":181000,"text":"For me the policing stood for power to correct,"},{"time":183000,"text":"power to prevent and power to detect."},{"time":186000,"text":"This is something like a new definition ever given in policing in India --"},{"time":189000,"text":"the power to prevent."},{"time":191000,"text":"Because normally it was always said, power to detect, and that's it,"},{"time":193000,"text":"or power to punish."},{"time":195000,"text":"But I decided no, it's a power to prevent,"},{"time":198000,"text":"because that's what I learned when I was growing up."},{"time":200000,"text":"How do I prevent the 10 and never make it more than 10?"},{"time":203000,"text":"So this was how it came into my service,"},{"time":206000,"text":"and it was different from the men."},{"time":208000,"text":"I didn't want to make it different from the men, but it was different,"},{"time":211000,"text":"because this was the way I was different."},{"time":214000,"text":"And I redefined policing concepts in India."},{"time":217000,"text":"I'm going to take you on two journeys,"},{"time":219000,"text":"my policing journey and my prison journey."},{"time":221000,"text":"What you see, if you see the title"},{"time":224000,"text":"called \"PM's car held.\""},{"time":226000,"text":"This was the first time a prime minister of India"},{"time":229000,"text":"was given a parking ticket."},{"time":231000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":233000,"text":"That's the first time in India,"},{"time":235000,"text":"and I can tell you, that's the last time you're hearing about it."},{"time":238000,"text":"It'll never happen again in India,"},{"time":240000,"text":"because now it was once and forever."},{"time":243000,"text":"And the rule was, because I was sensitive,"},{"time":245000,"text":"I was compassionate, I was very sensitive to injustice,"},{"time":248000,"text":"and I was very pro-justice."},{"time":250000,"text":"That's the reason, as a woman, I joined the Indian Police Service."},{"time":252000,"text":"I had other options, but I didn't choose them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":254000,"text":"So I'm going to move on."},{"time":256000,"text":"This is about tough policing, equal policing."},{"time":258000,"text":"Now I was known as \"here's a woman that's not going to listen.\""},{"time":261000,"text":"So I was sent to all indiscriminate postings,"},{"time":263000,"text":"postings which others would say no."},{"time":265000,"text":"I now went to a prison assignment as a police officer."},{"time":268000,"text":"Normally police officers don't want to do prison."},{"time":270000,"text":"They sent me to prison to lock me up,"},{"time":272000,"text":"thinking, \"Now there will be no cars"},{"time":274000,"text":"and no VIPs to be given tickets to."},{"time":276000,"text":"Let's lock her up.\""},{"time":278000,"text":"Here I got a prison assignment."},{"time":280000,"text":"This was a prison assignment which was one big den of criminals."},{"time":283000,"text":"Obviously, it was."},{"time":285000,"text":"But 10,000 men,"},{"time":287000,"text":"of which only 400 were women -- 10,000 --"},{"time":290000,"text":"9,000 plus about 600"},{"time":292000,"text":"were men."},{"time":294000,"text":"Terrorists, rapists,"},{"time":296000,"text":"burglars, gangsters --"},{"time":298000,"text":"some of them I'd sent to jail"},{"time":300000,"text":"as a police officer outside."},{"time":302000,"text":"And then how did I deal with them?"},{"time":304000,"text":"The first day when I went in,"},{"time":306000,"text":"I didn't know how to look at them."},{"time":308000,"text":"And I said, \"Do you pray?\" When I looked at the group, I said, \"Do you pray?\""},{"time":311000,"text":"They saw me as a young, short woman wearing a pathan suit."},{"time":313000,"text":"I said, \"Do you pray?\""},{"time":315000,"text":"And they didn't say anything."},{"time":317000,"text":"I said, \"Do you pray? Do you want to pray?\""},{"time":319000,"text":"They said, \"Yes.\" I said, \"All right, let's pray.\""},{"time":322000,"text":"I prayed for them, and things started to change."},{"time":324000,"text":"This is a visual of education inside the prison."}]},{"cues":[{"time":327000,"text":"Friends, this has never happened,"},{"time":329000,"text":"where everybody in the prison studies."},{"time":331000,"text":"I started this with community support."},{"time":333000,"text":"Government had no budget."},{"time":335000,"text":"It was one of the finest, largest volunteerism"},{"time":337000,"text":"in any prison in the world."},{"time":339000,"text":"This was initiated in Delhi prison."},{"time":341000,"text":"You see one sample"},{"time":343000,"text":"of a prisoner teaching a class."},{"time":346000,"text":"These are hundreds of classes."},{"time":348000,"text":"Nine to eleven, every prisoner went into the education program --"},{"time":351000,"text":"the same den in which they thought"},{"time":353000,"text":"they would put me behind the bar and things would be forgotten."},{"time":356000,"text":"We converted this into an ashram --"},{"time":358000,"text":"from a prison to an ashram through education."},{"time":361000,"text":"I think that's the bigger change."},{"time":363000,"text":"It was the beginning of a change."},{"time":365000,"text":"Teachers were prisoners. Teachers were volunteers."},{"time":368000,"text":"Books came from donated schoolbooks."},{"time":370000,"text":"Stationery was donated."},{"time":372000,"text":"Everything was donated,"},{"time":374000,"text":"because there was no budget of education for the prison."},{"time":377000,"text":"Now if I'd not done that,"},{"time":379000,"text":"it would have been a hellhole."}]},{"cues":[{"time":381000,"text":"That's the second landmark."},{"time":383000,"text":"I want to show you some moments of history in my journey,"},{"time":385000,"text":"which probably you would never ever get to see anywhere in the world."},{"time":388000,"text":"One, the numbers you'll never get to see."},{"time":390000,"text":"Secondly, this concept."},{"time":392000,"text":"This was a meditation program inside the prison"},{"time":394000,"text":"of over 1,000 prisoners."},{"time":396000,"text":"One thousand prisoners who sat in meditation."},{"time":398000,"text":"This was one of the most courageous steps"},{"time":401000,"text":"I took as a prison governor."},{"time":403000,"text":"And this is what transformed."},{"time":405000,"text":"You want to know more about this,"},{"time":407000,"text":"go and see this film, \"Doing Time, Doing Vipassana.\""},{"time":410000,"text":"You will hear about it, and you will love it."},{"time":412000,"text":"And write to me on KiranBedi.com,"},{"time":414000,"text":"and I'll respond to you."},{"time":416000,"text":"Let me show you the next slide."},{"time":418000,"text":"I took the same concept of mindfulness,"},{"time":420000,"text":"because, why did I bring meditation into the Indian prison?"},{"time":423000,"text":"Because crime is a product of a distorted mind."},{"time":426000,"text":"It was distortion of mind which needed to be addressed to control."},{"time":429000,"text":"Not by preaching, not by telling,"},{"time":431000,"text":"not by reading, but by addressing your mind."},{"time":433000,"text":"I took the same thing to the police,"},{"time":435000,"text":"because police, equally, were prisoners of their minds,"},{"time":438000,"text":"and they felt as if it was \"we\" and \"they,\""},{"time":440000,"text":"and that the people don't cooperate."},{"time":442000,"text":"This worked."}]},{"cues":[{"time":444000,"text":"This is a feedback box called a petition box."},{"time":446000,"text":"This is a concept which I introduced"},{"time":448000,"text":"to listen to complaints, listen to grievances."},{"time":451000,"text":"This was a magic box."},{"time":453000,"text":"This was a sensitive box."},{"time":455000,"text":"This is how a prisoner drew how they felt about the prison."},{"time":458000,"text":"If you see somebody in the blue --"},{"time":460000,"text":"yeah, this guy --"},{"time":462000,"text":"he was a prisoner, and he was a teacher."},{"time":464000,"text":"And you see, everybody's busy. There was no time to waste."}]},{"cues":[{"time":467000,"text":"Let me wrap it up."},{"time":469000,"text":"I'm currently into movements,"},{"time":471000,"text":"movements of education"},{"time":473000,"text":"of the under-served children,"},{"time":475000,"text":"which is thousands -- India is all about thousands."},{"time":478000,"text":"Secondly is about the anti-corruption movement in India."},{"time":480000,"text":"That's a big way"},{"time":482000,"text":"we, as a small group of activists,"},{"time":484000,"text":"have drafted an ombudsman bill for the government of India."},{"time":487000,"text":"Friends, you will hear a lot about it."},{"time":490000,"text":"That's the movement at the moment I'm driving,"},{"time":492000,"text":"and that's the movement and ambition of my life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":497000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":499000,"text":"Thank you. Thank you very much. Thank you."},{"time":502000,"text":"Thank you. Thank you. Thank you."}]}]}